# ============================================
# Cortex AML — Render Environment Variables
# ============================================
# Set these in Render Dashboard → Service → Environment

# ─── API Service (cortex-aml-api) ────────────
# DATABASE_URL          → Auto-linked from Render PostgreSQL
# SECRET_KEY            → Auto-generated by Render Blueprint
# CORS_ORIGINS          → https://cortex-aml-web.onrender.com
# OPENAI_API_KEY        → Your OpenAI API key (optional)
# NEWS_API_KEY          → Your NewsAPI key (optional)
# ENVIRONMENT           → production (set by blueprint)
# DEBUG                 → false (set by blueprint)

# ─── Web Service (cortex-aml-web) ────────────
# NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL   → https://cortex-aml-api.onrender.com/api/v1
# NODE_ENV              → production (set by blueprint)
